attributionInfo.brokerName: Coldwell Banker Howard Perry and Walston N Raleigh
Coldwell Banker Howard Perry and Walston N Raleigh

data.description: Wow! Magnificent 2 story home with a side entry garage with no HOA dues. Lovely community in the perfect location! Near shopping, major Wilson corridors and a park. Neighborhood is just the right size! Large entry foyer leads you to the first floor with formal areas. family room has a stone fire place for cozy winter evenings. Master bedroom is huge with a large walk in closet. Lots of potential for expanding home with unfinished bonus room. New HVAC in 2022 and new hot water heater in 2023.
